---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclaimer"
  description="How affiliate relationships work on The Wine Guide."
  noindex
>
  <div class="legal-wrap">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: 10 May 2026</p>

    <div class="legal-body">

      <p>The Wine Guide participates in affiliate programmes. This page explains what that means and how it affects the content you read.</p>

      <h2>What is an affiliate link?</h2>
      <p>Some links on this site are affiliate links. When you click one and make a purchase, I may earn a small commission from the retailer. The price you pay is exactly the same whether or not you use an affiliate link — commissions are paid by the retailer, not added to your purchase.</p>

      <h2>Which programmes does this site participate in?</h2>

      <h3>Amazon Associates</h3>
      <p>The Wine Guide is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising programme designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com and its regional equivalents (including Amazon.com.au, Amazon.co.uk, etc.).</p>

      <h3>wine.com</h3>
      <p>This site also participates in the wine.com affiliate programme. Some wine recommendations link directly to product pages on wine.com. If you purchase through one of these links, I may receive a commission.</p>

      <h2>Does this influence recommendations?</h2>
      <p>No. Affiliate relationships do not influence which wines I recommend or how I write about them. I recommend wines I genuinely believe are worth buying. A wine I dislike will not appear here simply because it pays a higher commission — that would defeat the entire purpose of this site.</p>
      <p>Occasionally a wine I want to recommend is not available on an affiliate platform. In those cases I still include it because the recommendation matters more than the commission.</p>

      <h2>FTC and ASA disclosure compliance</h2>
      <p>In accordance with the US Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines and the UK Advertising Standards Authority (ASA) rules on disclosure, I am required to clearly disclose any material connection between this site and the products or services recommended. Affiliate links represent such a connection. This disclaimer serves as that disclosure.</p>
      <p>Where individual articles contain affiliate links, they are marked with a disclosure notice at the top of the page.</p>

      <h2>GDPR and cookies</h2>
      <p>When you click an affiliate link, the destination site (Amazon or wine.com) may set cookies on your device to track the referral. I have no control over how those sites use cookies. Please refer to their respective privacy policies for details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=468496" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Amazon Privacy Notice</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.wine.com/v6/footer/privacypolicy.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">wine.com Privacy Policy</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about how affiliate links work on this site, email: <a href="mailto:claire.bennett@wineguide.co">claire.bennett@wineguide.co</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-wrap {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 24px 96px;
  }

  .legal-wrap h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #1a1713;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }

  .legal-meta {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8a8177;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
  }

  .legal-body {
    color: #3a3530;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-body p {
    margin: 0 0 1.25em;
  }

  .legal-body h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1713;
    margin: 2.5em 0 0.75em;
    padding-top: 2em;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e0d4;
  }

  .legal-body h3 {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #5c3d2e;
    margin: 1.75em 0 0.5em;
  }

  .legal-body ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.25em 1.5em;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .legal-body li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4em;
  }

  .legal-body a {
    color: #8a4a2f;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .legal-body a:hover {
    color: #5c3d2e;
  }

  .legal-body strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1713;
  }
</style>
